Name: reload
Version: 0.2
Summary: Reload a program if any file in current directory changes.
Home-page: https://github.com/loomchild/reload
Author: Jarek Lipski
Author-email: pub@loomchild.net
License: MIT
Description: Reload
        
        This program starts given program and reloads it whenever any file in current directory changes.
        Files can be excluded by putting them in .reloadignore file.
        
        
